headline: Phillips 66 to announce fourth-quarter and full-year financial results
summary: HOUSTON, December 18, 2024--Phillips 66 will host a webcast at noon ET on Friday, Jan. 31, 2025, to discuss the company’s fourth-quarter and full-year 2024 financial results.
